  "importantNotice": {
    "de": "Um den Bonus des Sets <b>Verhexungen von Ephedrya</b> zu erhalten, steckt euch einen dieser Ringe an:\n\n<color=#ffffff>• {{itemHover,27547::Grausamkeit von Belladonna}}</color>\n<color=#ffffff>• {{itemHover,27548::Bitterkeit von Belladonna}}</color>\n<color=#ffffff>• {{itemHover,27549::Zärtlichkeit von Belladonna}}</color>",
    "en": "To get the <b>Evils of Ephedrya</b> set bonus, equip one of these rings:\n\n<color=#ffffff>• {{itemHover,27547::Belladonna's Cruelty}}</color>\n<color=#ffffff>• {{itemHover,27548::Belladonna's Bitterness}}</color>\n<color=#ffffff>• {{itemHover,27549::Belladonna's Tenderness}}</color>",
    "es": "Para disfrutar del bonus del set <b>Maleficios de Efedria</b>, equípate uno de estos anillos:\n\n<color=#ffffff>• {{itemHover,27547::Crueldad de Belladona}}</color>\n<color=#ffffff>• {{itemHover,27548::Amargura de Belladona}}</color>\n<color=#ffffff>• {{itemHover,27549::Ternura de Belladona}}</color>",
    "fr": "",
    "id": "1104193",
    "pt": "Para se beneficiar do bônus do conjunto <b>Maldições de Ephedrya</b>, equipe um destes anéis:\n\n<color=#ffffff>• {{itemHover,27547::Crueldade de Beladona}}</color>\n<color=#ffffff>• {{itemHover,27548::Amargor de Beladona}}</color>\n<color=#ffffff>• {{itemHover,27549::Ternura de Beladona}}</color>"
  },
